{"tid":973934,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"奧地利傳感器公司與中國公司合作開發3D人臉識別","createTime":"2019-01-08T13:33:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-09T01:52:44.000Z","uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a4fca0d4c87207bc34cdd2c5b4084a6a48ed65d7","tid":973934,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T13:33:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://gdb.voanews.com/373B0C0B-E83B-420A-A846-B5AC0B2BEFFB_w1023_r1_s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgdb.voanews.com%2F373B0C0B-E83B-420A-A846-B5AC0B2BEFFB_w1023_r1_s.jpg&h=3f514ba8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n參觀者在深圳舉行的中國公安展會上體驗人臉識別技術。（2017年10月30日）<br />\n<br />\n奧地利傳感器公司艾邁斯AMS在努力降低對美國蘋果公司的依賴的同時，將與中國軟件開發商曠視科技(Face++)合作，為智能手機開發新的3D人臉識別功能。<br />\n<br />\n目前為蘋果手機提供光傳感器的AMS，因蘋果最新一代手機銷售低於預期，尤其是在中國市場，面臨巨大壓力，被迫調低業績預期，股票去年下跌了75%。<br />\n<br />\n據報導，業內人士表示，技術上的挑戰使得艾邁斯AMS很難在安卓系統手機上實現多樣化，但與北京曠視科技的合作，或有助於技術突破，降低AMS對蘋果的依賴。曠視科技此次將提供軟件處理AMS傳感器提供的光數據，用於手機。<br />\n<br />\n艾邁斯公司表示，與曠視科技的合作表明，3D傳感解決方案逐漸成為主流，將應用於消費、汽車、醫療和工業電子等領域。AMS公司的股票受該消息刺激，在周一的交易中上漲超過10%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voachinese.com/a/AMS-Partners-China-To-Develop-Face-Recognition-Tech-20190107/4731820.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voachinese.com%2Fa%2FAMS-Partners-China-To-Develop-Face-Recognition-Tech-20190107%2F4731820.html&d=YzhzPCpgBYRVwF9Kd3lPztibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=6ab749aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.voachinese.com/a/AMS-Partners-China-To-Develop-Face-Recognition-Tech-20190107/4731820.html</a>"},{"pid":"644aebd6c6090402576bdac93a67f0b80bf6bbbc","tid":973934,"uid":171866,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T01:36:32.000Z","msg":"雪亮工程<br />\n班西人到底有無人性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a1fc0a301637e51ff9aea6cf66799879146f964","tid":973934,"uid":6347,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T01:50:43.000Z","msg":"同中國合作用黎政治迫害人<br />\n知唔知共產黨開左集中營<br />\n有冇人性架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"578114b84e4dd7d6ccc9af8e227d514e1bc7b77f","tid":973934,"uid":48531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a1fc0a301637e51ff9aea6cf66799879146f964","tid":973934,"uid":6347,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T01:50:43.000Z","msg":"同中國合作用黎政治迫害人<br />\n知唔知共產黨開左集中營<br />\n有冇人性架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T01:52:44.000Z","msg":"迫害又中國人又有錢賺 有乜所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}